    "name": "HYPERBEAT",
    "steam_appid": 2263360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/9fff043ed0056b9564ae70980fa28c1f.poster.avif?t=1766090994\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/9fff043ed0056b9564ae70980fa28c1f.webm?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/9fff043ed0056b9564ae70980fa28c1f.mp4?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the Wellspring, a moment of serenity in a world that waits for no one. In <strong>HYPERBEAT</strong>, embark as a knight among an order chasing their highest potential. Master fast-paced, precision rhythm gameplay with a completely original 90-minute soundtrack. Uncover the intertwined stories of an ensemble cast—What will you find at the peak of what you’re chasing?   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/3199a39057e41e269177e6ed84c09e3d.poster.avif?t=1766090994\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/3199a39057e41e269177e6ed84c09e3d.webm?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/3199a39057e41e269177e6ed84c09e3d.mp4?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Discover the order through their work. Play your way with full support for controller, mouse, and tablet. <strong>HYPERBEAT</strong> features sixty handcrafted rhythm charts—three difficulties for each song—meaning there’s something for everyone, for every part of their journey. Thoughtful accessibility options ensure that even those new to rhythm games can play.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/124f5804b37db9501d68dad6b6ee1523.poster.avif?t=1766090994\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/124f5804b37db9501d68dad6b6ee1523.webm?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/124f5804b37db9501d68dad6b6ee1523.mp4?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Dress up your journey with unlockable cosmetics earned through a collect-a-thon. With over 100 items to discover, from outfit tweaks to complete style overhauls, develop your own unique style within the order. Customize the palette of the game itself too—even the colors of the notes—to match your mood. And as you grow closer to other members of the cast, you’ll receive unique items that carry a piece of their story.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/51dff7842fb7ef03535cbb52dd784f8f.poster.avif?t=1766090994\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/51dff7842fb7ef03535cbb52dd784f8f.webm?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/51dff7842fb7ef03535cbb52dd784f8f.mp4?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Step into the lives of an ensemble cast whose stories unfold as you connect with them. Through a “social link” system, the more you engage with their work, the more you discover who they are. Take a moment to gather at the Wellspring’s bar, a space to linger, share, and deepen bonds—where quiet conversations reveal the threads that tie everyone together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/9ef6f44740b32773cd1b30ae4fe9616b.poster.avif?t=1766090994\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/9ef6f44740b32773cd1b30ae4fe9616b.webm?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/9ef6f44740b32773cd1b30ae4fe9616b.mp4?t=1766090994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <strong>HYPERBEAT</strong> lives beyond its own songs with full support to create and share your own charts. Put your own music in the game or download others’ off the community workshop.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No rhythm game experience required! Play at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Completely original soundtrack with over 90-minutes of music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story mode  with handcrafted levels, and free play until your hands hurt. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a visually stunning space and meet the KNIGHTS that embody the WELLSPRING.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your KNIGHT as you progress through the adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom charts with workshop integration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced rhythm gameplay with both mouse, controller, and tablet support. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulties and accessibility options to tailor your gaming experience to your preferences. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
